com.mapbox.services.android.telemetry

Class TelemetryLocationReceiver

  • java.lang.Object
    • android.content.BroadcastReceiver
      • com.mapbox.services.android.telemetry.TelemetryLocationReceiver

  • public class TelemetryLocationReceiver
extends BroadcastReceiver
    The TelemetryService will register for updates sent to this TelemetryLocationReceiver. Messages are sent locally using a LocalBroadcastManager.
